window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Marly refuses to believe her friend Rae committed suicide. Even though her wrists were slit, Marly knows her beautiful, vibrant bestie would never do that.</p> <p>Even though the two had drifted apart, Marly and Rae made a blood promise long ago. Even in death, Marly intends to honor that vow.</p> <p>Determined to find Rae’s killer, Marly faces a long list of potential suspects. It seems everyone has secrets or lies that they are covering up...including the boy she loves.&nbsp;</p> <p>Can Marly uncover the murderer’s identity before she becomes the next victim?</p>"; 
